@div segment A

$ (unknown no. of lines missing)
A.1. X [...] IL₂ [...] mu-na-sug₂-sug₂-ge#-[eš]
#lem: X; X; X; X; sug[stand]
#etcsl: line-id=A.1

A.2. {d}nin-isin₂{si}-na nin me gal-gal-la-ra#
#lem: Ninisinak[1]DN; nin[lady]; me[Being]; gal[big]
#etcsl: line-id=A.2

A.3. me kug me sikil-la šu he₂-en-na-du₇-du₇
#lem: me[Being]; kug[purify]; me[Being]; sikil[pure]; šu[hand]; du[perfect]
#etcsl: line-id=A.3

A.4. me-ni me an-ne₂# saŋ-e-eš rig₇-ga-ni
#lem: me[Being]; me[Being]; An[1]DN; saŋ[head]; rig[donate]
#etcsl: line-id=A.4

A.5. kur gal {d}en-lil₂-le nam-e-eš mu-ni-in-tar
